Informative interview with Dr. Lucero and Dr. Yoon that will likely address many of your questions. @StamfordMoms

Also mark your calendar for the Parent Pop Up Webinars scheduled for Monday.
shared_text:
stamfordmoms.com
August 14 at 9:35 AM ·

As we look ahead to another unusual school year, many Stamford families are deciding whether the Hybrid Model or Distance Learning is best for our families Stamford Public Schools!

To help answer some of your questions, I chatted with Stamford Public School Superintendent Dr. Tamu Lucero and Medical Advisor to the City of Stamford Dr. Henry Yoon about the upcoming school year.

We talked about how the hybrid schedule will work, what the buses will look like, mask breaks at school and childcare for working parents among many other topics. Check out the video above!

#stamfordmoms #stamfordct #stamfordkids #stamfordfamilies #stamforkids #stamfordfamilies #stamfordstudents #stamfordschools #stamfordpublicschools #givingmomsthegiftoftime #makingmommyingeasy #hybridlearning #distancelearning
